West Bengal
Nov 23, 2014
Murder
Description:
			A woman was found dead with stab injuries in her body in her house in DumDum area of North 24 Parganas district today, police said.

A 55-year-old woman was found dead in her room with stab injuries in her body by her son in their Ghughu danga phari residence in DumDum area.

Some jewellery was also found missing from the dead woman's room, the police said adding a complaint has been lodged and we are investigating the matter.


